description: Injured in an explosion in Afghanistan while saving an entire battery of men, Glen Denton spent ten years in a coma kept alive only by The bio genetic work of his father. Upon awakening he finds his body is now able to alter its Harmonics as a defense mechanism giving him abilities that enable him to create percussion blast and also protect him against impacts. He uses his new found powers in the defense of freedom.

Read exclusive previews of the biggest event of 2012 - Avengers vs X-Men - including pages from Avengers vs X-Men #0 and #1. Plus, meet the major players from AVX with character bios of the Avengers, X-Men, and wildcards. Also Includes The road to A vs. X.
